Package: BBMeth
Title: BBMeth: beta-binomial estimation of methylation changes from
	bisulfite-sequencing data.
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Devon P. Ryan (DZNE Bonn)
Maintainer: Devon P. Ryan <devon.ryan@dzne.de>
Description: Estimate mean and overdispersion of count data from high-throughput
	bisulfite sequencing experiments and test for resulting changes using a
	beta-binomial distribution
License: GPL (>=3)
Imports: BiocGenerics, rtracklayer
Depends: GenomicRanges, IRanges, BiocParallel
Suggests: ggplot2, GenomicFeatures, bsseqData, bumphunter
biocViews: Software, DNAMethylation, DifferentialMethylation, Sequencing, MethylSeq
